    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3fd9cabb-23b5-49a5-b0a0-8cf48301b7fd">
                Mr. Edmund Harvey
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3fd9cabb-23b5-49a5-b0a0-8cf48301b7fd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1943-07-14/debates/0b941883-0cb9-4922-a632-006b6a4e6694/ElectoralReform#contribution-3fd9cabb-23b5-49a5-b0a0-8cf48301b7fd">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Would not such a discussion by Parliament be much more profitable if there could be a preliminary inquiry such as is suggested in the Question?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3fd9cabb-23b5-49a5-b0a0-8cf48301b7fd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
